extras.diff:
--- /workspace/dosage_recommender.py
+++ /workspace/dosage_recommender.py
@@ -1 +1,16 @@
-
+def suggest_dosage(data: dict) -> str:
+    base_dose = 50  # Default starting dose
+
+    # Increase for high stress (7+ on 10-point scale)
+    if data.get('stress_level', 0) >= 7:
+        base_dose = 100
+
+    # Reduce for elderly patients
+    if data.get('age', 0) >= 65:
+        base_dose = max(25, base_dose // 2)
+
+    # Special consideration for high-stress occupations
+    if data.get('occupation', '').lower() in ['grad student', 'first responder']:
+        base_dose = min(150, base_dose + 25)
+
+    return f"Start Sertraline {base_dose}mg daily, adjust in 4-6 weeks based on response"
